#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Step-By-Step Tutorial"
msgstr "Vadnica po korakih"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter, &stage; is introduced using a simple tutorial. We shall "
"walk through the most basic steps that are involved in creating a "
"presentation, and adding some basic effects."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju je &stage; predstavljen s preprosto vadnico. Sprehodili se "
"bomo skozi najosnovnejše korake, ki so vključeni v ustvarjanje predstavitve "
"in dodajanje nekaterih osnovnih učinkov."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start a new document"
msgstr "Začni nov dokument"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "When you start &stage;, the usual &calligra; startup dialog appears."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &stage;, se običajno prikaže &calligra; z zagonskim pogovornim "
"oknom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>&calligra;</guilabel> startup dialog"
msgstr "Zagonsko pogovorno okno <guilabel>&calligra;</guilabel>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &calligra; startup dialog"
msgstr "&calligra; zagonsko pogovorno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Screen</guilabel> on the left then select the template "
"labeled <guilabel>Empty</guilabel> (highlighted in blue in the screenshot "
"above) by clicking on it. You can check <guilabel>Always use this template</"
"guilabel> to make it the default template."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Zaslon</guilabel> na levi in nato izberite predlogo z "
"oznako <guilabel>Prazno</guilabel> (označeno z modro na zgornjem posnetku "
"zaslona), tako da kliknete nanjo. Odkljukate lahko <guilabel>Vedno uporabi "
"to predlogo</guilabel>, da postane privzeta predloga."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now click <guibutton>Use This Template</guibutton>. This brings up the slide "
"editor window, where you can view and edit the slides (and objects contained "
"in them) in your document."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj kliknite <guibutton>Uporabi to predlogo</guibutton>. S tem se prikaže "
"okno urejevalnika prosojnic, kjer si lahko ogledate in urejate prosojnice "
"(in predmete, ki jih vsebujejo) v vašem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the moment, we just have one empty slide, so select the upper left slide "
"with the single text box from the <guilabel>Slide Layouts</guilabel> docker."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno imamo samo eno prazno prosojnico, zato izberite zgornjo "
"levoprosojnico z enim besedilnim poljem v oknu <guilabel>Postavitve "
"prosojnic</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click the text box. The cursor changes to a vertical bar to show that "
"you can now type some text."
msgstr ""
"Dvokliknite besedilno polje. Kazalec se spremeni v navpično vrstico, ki "
"kaže, da lahko zdaj vnesete nekaj besedila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The text insertion cursor</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kazalec za vstavljanje besedila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The text insertion cursor</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kazalec za vstavljanje besedila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go ahead, type some text!"
msgstr "Kar naprej, vnesite besedilo!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding text</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodajanje besedila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding text</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodajanje besedila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click away from the text to de-select the text box when you are done typing."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate s tipkanjem, kliknite proč od besedila, da počistite polje z "
"besedilom."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a new page"
msgstr "Dodajte novo stran"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's now add a new slide to our document. To do so, click the "
"<guimenu>Slide</guimenu> menu, and then click on <guimenuitem>Insert Slide</"
"guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj pa dodamo novo prosojnico v naš dokument. To naredite tako, da kliknete "
"meni <guimenu>Prosojnica</guimenu> in nato kliknete <guimenuitem>Vstavi "
"prosojnico</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now we can decide what the new slide should look like. This time, select one "
"column layout (highlighted in blue.)"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj se lahko odločimo, kako naj bo nova prosojnica videti. Tokrat izberite "
"eno postavitev stolpca (označeno z modro.)"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Choosing a layout for the new page</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbira postavitve za novo stran</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Choosing a layout for the new page</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbira postavitve za novo stran</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The new slide layout now appears in the editing window. To change between "
"pages of your presentation, you can select slides in the pane to the left "
"(highlighted in blue for this screenshot)."
msgstr ""
"Nova postavitev prosojnice se zdaj prikaže v oknu za urejanje. Če želite "
"preklapljati med stranmi svoje predstavitve, lahko izberete prosojnice v "
"podoknu na levi (označeno z modro za ta posnetek zaslona)."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The newly inserted slide has two text boxes. There is one for a title, and "
"another to contain a bulleted list of items."
msgstr ""
"Na novo vstavljena prosojnica ima dve besedilni polji. Ena je za naslov, "
"druga pa vsebuje označeni seznam elementov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The new slide</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nova prosojnica</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The new slide</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nova prosojnica</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Double-click and type a title. Then double-click on the second text box with "
"the bullet. Type some text and end the paragraph by pressing the "
"<keycap>Enter</keycap> or <keycap>Return</keycap> key. As you type new "
"paragraphs, bullets automatically appear in front of them."
msgstr ""
"Dvokliknite in vnesite naslov. Nato dvokliknite drugo besedilno polje z "
"oznako. Vnesite besedilo in končajte odstavek s pritiskom tipke "
"<keycap>Enter</keycap> ali <keycap>Return</keycap>. Ko vnašate nove "
"odstavke, se pred njimi samodejno prikažejo oznake."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding text to the second slide</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodajanje besedila k drugi prosojnici</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding text to the second slide</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodajanje besedila k drugi prosojnici</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can de-select the text box by clicking away from it."
msgstr "Polje z besedilom lahko prekličete tako, da kliknete stran od njega."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a picture"
msgstr "Vstavite sliko"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's go back to the first slide now. Use the list of slides on the left of "
"your screen."
msgstr ""
"Vrnimo se zdaj k prvi prosojnici. Uporabite seznam prosojnic na levi strani "
"zaslona."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section, we'll liven our presentation up a bit by adding a nice logo "
"to the title page. To do so, the first step is to enable the <guilabel>Add "
"Shape</guilabel> docker using <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Dockers</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku bomo našo predstavitev nekoliko poživili z dodajanjem lepega "
"logotipa na naslovno stran. Če želite to narediti, je prvi korak, da "
"omogočite okence <guilabel>Dodaj obliko</guilabel> z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sidrišča</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now select Image in the <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel> docker and click with "
"the &LMB; where you want to place the loge in it's original size or draw a "
"rectangle with the left mouse (click the &LMB; and keep the button pressed) "
"to specify the position and size for the logo."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj izberite Slika v orodju <guilabel>Dodaj obliko</guilabel> in kliknite z "
"&LMB; kamor želite postaviti ložo v izvirni velikosti ali narišite "
"pravokotnik z levo miško (kliknite &LMB; in držite gumb pritisnjen), da "
"določite položaj in velikost loga."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A file selection dialog appears. To learn about this or other standard &kde; "
"dialog boxes in detail, please consult the &kde; documentation. You can "
"browse by clicking on <guiicon>folder</guiicon> icons or by using the "
"<guiicon>browser</guiicon> style buttons on the toolbar. Clicking the "
"<guiicon>up arrow</guiicon> takes you up one folder level."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže se pogovorno okno za izbiro datoteke. Če želite izvedeti več o tem "
"ali drugem standardu &kde; podrobneje o pogovornih oknih si oglejte &kde; "
"dokumentacijo. Brskate lahko s klikom na ikone <guiicon>mape</guiicon> ali z "
"uporabo gumbov za slog <guiicon>brskalnika</guiicon> v orodni vrstici. Če "
"kliknete <guiicon>puščico navzgor</guiicon>, se pomaknete eno raven mape "
"navzgor."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select a file and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr "Izberite datoteko in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now the image is inserted in the slide and there are selection handles "
"(little squares) visible around the border of the graphic."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj je slika vstavljena v prosojnico in okoli roba grafike so vidne izbirne "
"ročice (majhni kvadratki)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The newly added image</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Novo dodana slika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The newly added image</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Novo dodana slika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place the mouse cursor anywhere in the middle of the logo, and drag it to "
"the middle of the title page. Then use the selection handles to resize it "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"Kazalec miške postavite kamor koli na sredino logotipa in ga povlecite na "
"sredino naslovne strani. Nato uporabite izbirne ročice, da pravilno "
"spremenite velikost."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "That's it. Now you have a picture on the title page!"
msgstr "To je vse. Zdaj imate sliko na naslovnici!"

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert a &calligra; object"
msgstr "Vstavite predmet &calligra;"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's insert another &calligra; object under the picture, for example a "
"chart."
msgstr "Vstavimo še en predmet &calligra; pod sliko na primer grafikon."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every &calligra; supported object can be embedded in a &stage; slide. Let's "
"choose a chart from the <guilabel>Add Shape</guilabel> docker."
msgstr ""
"Vsak &calligra; podprti predmet je mogoče vdelati v prosojnico &stage;. "
"Izberimo grafikon iz sidrišča <guilabel>Dodaj obliko</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guilabel>Chart</guilabel> and then outline with your mouse the area "
"you want to put your chart in on the &stage; slide."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <guilabel>Grafikon</guilabel> in nato z miško označite območje, "
"kamor želite postaviti svoj grafikon na prosojnico &stage;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select the area where to put the chart</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Izberite območje, kamor želite postaviti grafikon</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select the area where to put the chart</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izberite območje, kamor želite postaviti grafikon</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you release the mouse button, a template chart is added on the slide. "
"Whenever you work in the chart, its <guilabel>Tool Options</guilabel> appear "
"in the docker."
msgstr ""
"Ko spustite miškino tipko, se na prosojnico doda predloga grafikona. "
"Kadarkoli delate v grafikonu, se njegove <guilabel>Možnosti orodij</"
"guilabel> prikažejo v oknu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kchart; Tool Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kchart; Možnosti orodja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kchart; Tool Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kchart; Možnosti orodja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move, resize or even delete the embedded chart switch to the "
"<guibutton>Basic shape manipulation</guibutton> tool and click anywhere "
"within the chart area. It should now appear with a green border and with a "
"small yellow square at each corner and in the middle of each edge."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti, spremeniti velikost ali celo izbrisati vdelani "
"grafikon, preklopite na orodje <guibutton>Manipulacija osnovne oblike</"
"guibutton> in kliknite kjer koli znotraj območja grafikona. Zdaj bi se moral "
"pojaviti z zeleno obrobo in z majhnim rumenim kvadratom na vsakem vogalu in "
"na sredini vsakega roba."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you move the cursor over any of the squares it should change to a double "
"headed arrow. You can resize the chart by dragging one of these squares with "
"the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button pressed. To delete the "
"chart <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on one of the squares and "
"select <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če kazalec premaknete čez katerega koli kvadrata, se mora spremeniti v "
"dvosmerno puščico. Velikost grafikona lahko spremenite tako, da povlečete "
"enega od teh kvadratov s pritisnjeno <mousebutton>levo</mousebutton> tipko "
"miške. Če želite izbrisati grafikon, <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> "
"kliknite na enega od kvadratkov in izberite <guimenuitem>Izbriši</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move the chart move the cursor into the chart. The cursor should then "
"change to a cross, press the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button "
"and you will be able to drag the chart to where you want it to be."
msgstr ""
"Če želite premakniti grafikon, premaknite kazalec na grafikon. Kazalec naj "
"se nato spremeni v križec, pritisnite <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> gumb "
"miške in grafikon boste lahko potegnili na želeno mesto."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To restore the chart to its normal appearance simply click anywhere outside "
"of the chart area."
msgstr ""
"Če želite obnoviti običajen videz grafikona, preprosto kliknite kjer koli "
"zunaj območja grafikona."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the format of the chart itself <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
"click twice within the chart area. The chart <guilabel>Tools Options</"
"guilabel> should appear in the docker. You can then use these tools to edit "
"the chart properties like chart type, labels, axis and data."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti obliko samega grafikona, <mousebutton>levo</"
"mousebutton> dvakrat kliknite znotraj območja grafikona. Grafikon "
"<guilabel>Možnosti orodij</guilabel> bi se moral prikazati v oknu. Nato "
"lahko uporabite ta orodja za urejanje lastnosti grafikona, kot so vrsta "
"grafikona, oznake, osi in podatki."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click anywhere with the &LMB; outside the chart to go back to &stage; slide."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite kjer koli z &LMB; zunaj grafikona, da se vrnete na prosojnico "
"&stage;."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A single click on the chart will allow you to drag it to change its location "
"and also to drag the borders to make it bigger as with any other &stage; "
"object. Double click on the chart to get into &kchart; mode and modify any "
"of the chart property."
msgstr ""
"En sam klik na grafikon vam bo omogočil, da ga povlečete, da spremenite "
"njegovo lokacijo, in povlečete meje, da ga povečate, kot pri vseh drugih "
"predmetih &stage;. Dvokliknite grafikon, da odprete v načinu &kchart; in "
"spremenite katero koli lastnost grafikona."

#. Tag: title
#: tutorial.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the color of the title text"
msgstr "Spremenite barvo besedila naslova"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let's finish by changing the color of the title text from black to blue. To "
"do so, select the title text by double-clicking the text box and select the "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Zaključimo s spremembo barve besedila naslova iz črne v modro. To storite "
"tako, da izberete besedilo naslova tako, da dvokliknete besedilno polje in "
"izberete besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the color selector by clicking on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"22x22-actions-format-text-color.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> icon in the Text editing Tools Options "
"(this icon has a Text Color... tooltip)."
msgstr ""
"Odprite izbirnik barv s klikom na ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"22x22-actions-format-text-color.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> v Besedilo urejanje možnosti orodij (ta "
"ikona ima barvo besedila ... opis orodja)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:377 tutorial.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The color selector</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbirnik barv</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:380 tutorial.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The color selector</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbirnik barv</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the color to blue."
msgstr "Spremenite barvo v modro."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the color of the selected text to blue changes its appearance. The "
"exact color that highlighted text turns depends on your system color scheme."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje barve izbranega besedila v modro spremeni njegov videz. "
"Natančna barva, v katero se spremeni označeno besedilo, je odvisna od barvne "
"sheme vašega sistema."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Text color selection is also available on the <guilabel>Decorations</"
"guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Select Font</guilabel> dialog. Open this "
"dialog with <guimenuitem>Font</guimenuitem> in the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> "
"menu or context menu."
msgstr ""
"Izbira barve besedila je na voljo tudi na zavihku <guilabel>Okraski</"
"guilabel> pogovornega okna <guilabel>Izberi pisavo</guilabel>. Odprite to "
"pogovorno okno s <guimenuitem>Pisava</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Oblika</"
"guimenu> ali kontekstnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Now click away from the text to de-select it."
msgstr "Zdaj kliknite stran od besedila, da ga prekličete."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tutorial.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The finished title</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dokončan naslov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tutorial.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The finished title</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dokončan naslov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now that there are two slides, why not try a slide show! To start the slide "
"show, press the <guiicon>Start Presentation</guiicon> button in the toolbar. "
"The first slide should appear on your screen."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj, ko sta na voljo dve prosojnici, zakaj ne bi poskusili z "
"predstavitvijo! Za začetek predstavitve pritisnite gumb <guiicon>Začni "
"predstavitev</guiicon> v orodni vrstici. Na zaslonu se mora prikazati prva "
"prosojnica."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To advance from the first slide to the next, just click anywhere on the "
"screen, or use the <keycap>Page Down</keycap> key."
msgstr ""
"Če želite napredovati od prve prosojnice do naslednje, kliknite kjer koli na "
"zaslonu ali uporabite tipko <keycap>Page Down</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: tutorial.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid "To exit the slide show, press the &Esc; key."
msgstr "Za izhod iz predstavitve pritisnite tipko &Esc;."
